Title: Einhell EINTECL18LI TE-CL 18 Li H-Solo Power X-Change LED Torch 18V Bare Unit EINTECL18LI
Description:
The Einhell TE-CL 18 Li H-Solo Power X-Change LED Torch is equipped with a high-performance LED for extra bright light with a 280 Lumen output. Thanks to its low power consumption, the lamp provides prolonged lighting and optimum illumination with a swivelling lamp head.

The rugged housing with carry handle and soft grip make the lamp easy to transport. It can be hung up quickly and easily anywhere, thanks to its practical metal hook.

The TE-CL 18 Li H-Solo LED Torch is a member of the Einhell Power X-Change family and can be powered by all batteries from other Power X-Change family products.

Bare Unit, No Battery or Charger Supplied.

Specification

Light Output: 280 Lumens.
Weight: 0.22kg.
